      "notes": "Approved false Basic 1500000.0 2000000.0 500000.0 The Vacation Rental Certification Program (VRCP) utilizes revenue generated through the WC Ordinance 2023 03 directed certification of approximately 7,500 short term vacation rentals. As of the end of 2nd QTR FY 2025 net income is $687,483.50 and within glidepath of anticipated revenue for FY 2026 2027 to meet the requested expenditures. Per direction from BCC and County Administrator, the program will incrementally increase capacity for reviewal and approval of certifications through the upcoming FY. We continue to actively identify cost savings and operational efficiencies, which may result in decreased expenditures in the upcoming cycle."
